{"view":"article","slug":"lbl","category":"3x3","subcategory":null,"topDir":"3x3","title":{"en":"3x3 LBL Method (Layer-By-Layer)","zh":"三阶魔方层先法 (LBL)"},"content":{"en":"<p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/en/image2.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>3x3 LBL Method (Layer-By-Layer)</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td rowspan=\"3\"><p><strong><u>Notation</u></strong></p><p>Holding the cube in a fixed position, there are six sides that can be turned. A single letter denotes turning the specified face 90° clockwise. A letter followed by a prime (') symbol denotes a 90° turn counterclockwise. A letter followed by a 2 denotes a double turn.</p></td><td colspan=\"3\"><p>U (Up) - D (Down) - L (Left) - R (Right) - F (Front) - B (Back)</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/en/image4.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/en/image6.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/en/image8.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>U</strong> (Clockwise)</p></td><td><p><strong>U'</strong> (Counterclockwise)</p></td><td><p><strong>U2</strong> (Double Turns)</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td rowspan=\"2\"><p><strong><u>First Layer Cross</u></strong></p><p>Put white center on D face. Position 4 white edges around white center piece to create a cross. Make sure that the non-white stickers of edges also line up with their corresponding center pieces. </p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/en/image10.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/en/image12.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/en/image14.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>Solved</strong></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R D R' D' R\"><strong>R D R' D' R</strong></span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"F' D R' D'\"><strong>F' D R' D'</strong></span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td rowspan=\"2\"><p><strong><u>First Layer Corners</u></strong></p><p>Find white corner piece in U layer. If there is no such piece, then execute <strong>R U R' </strong>from any angle.</p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/en/image16.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/en/image18.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/en/image20.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R U R'\"><strong>R U R'</strong></span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"U R U' R'\"><strong>U R U' R'</strong></span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"(R U2' R' U') R U R'\"><strong>(R U2' R' U') R U R'</strong></span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td rowspan=\"2\"><p><strong><u>Middle Layer Edges</u></strong></p><p>Holding top layer edge at the front and matching its front sticker with the center, it will either need to go to the right or left position. If an edge is misoriented or stuck in the wrong position, take it out by inserting another edge into its position.</p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/en/image22.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/en/image24.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"(U' L' U L)\"><strong>(U' L' U L) </strong></span></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"(U F U' F')\"><strong>(U F U' F')</strong></span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"(U R U' R')\"><strong>(U R U' R') </strong></span></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"(U' F' U F)\"><strong>(U' F' U F)</strong></span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td rowspan=\"2\"><p><strong><u>Last Layer EO</u></strong></p><p>Check the pattern of oriented edges.</p><p>[abbreviation: E (Edge) C (Corner) </p><p>O (Orientation) P (Permutation)]</p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/en/image26.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/en/image28.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/en/image30.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"F R U R' U' F'\"><strong>F R U R' U' F'</strong></span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"F R U R' U' F'\"><strong>F R U R' U' F'</strong></span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"F R U R' U' F'\"><strong>F R U R' U' F'</strong></span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td rowspan=\"3\"><p><strong><u>Last Layer CO</u></strong></p><p>Check the number of oriented corners.</p></td><td><p><strong>0 CO</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>2 CO</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>1 CO</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/en/image32.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/en/image34.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/en/image36.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R U R' U R U2' R'\"><strong>R U R' U R U2' R'</strong></span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R U R' U R U2' R'\"><strong>R U R' U R U2' R'</strong></span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R U R' U R U2' R'\"><strong>R U R' U R U2' R'</strong></span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td rowspan=\"2\"><p><strong><u>Last Layer CP</u></strong></p><p>Correctly align two corners on the left. If there are no matching corners initially, execute from any angle.</p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/en/image38.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td rowspan=\"2\"><p><u>Last Layer EP</u></p><p>Move a block where an edge is solved to the back. If there is no block initially, execute from any angle.</p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/en/image40.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"(R U R' F') (R U R' U') (R' F R2 U' R')\"><strong>(R U R' F') (R U R' U') (R' F R2 U' R')</strong></span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"(R U' R U) R U\"><strong>(R U' R U) R U </strong></span></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"(R U' R' U') R2\"><strong>(R U' R' U') R2</strong></span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td rowspan=\"2\"><p><strong><u>底棱归层</u></strong></p><p>在U或E层找到白棱,  通过y转体将其放在R层,  转D层使DF棱不是白棱 (图中用紫色表示),  然后转R使之前找到的白棱移动到D层. 重复上述步骤,  直到让所有4个白棱都位于D层.</p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/en/image42.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/en/image44.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/en/image46.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>R</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>R'</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>R2</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td rowspan=\"2\"><p><strong><u>底棱翻</u></strong></p><p>使4个白棱的白格位于底层..</p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/en/image48.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td rowspan=\"2\"><p><strong><u>底棱序</u></strong></p><p>转D层使至少两个棱归位,  然后做公式.</p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/en/image50.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/en/image12.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/en/image10.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"F' D R'\"><strong>F' D R'</strong></span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"M2' U2 M2'\"><strong>M2' U2 M2'</strong></span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R D R' D' R\"><strong>R D R' D' R</strong></span></p></td><td><p><strong>十字完成</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td rowspan=\"2\"><p><strong><u>角位置</u></strong></p><p>将两个角块在左侧归位, 做公式. 若没有, 就在任意方向做公式. </p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/en/image38.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td rowspan=\"2\"><p><strong><u>棱位置</u></strong></p><p>将归位的棱块放到背面, 做公式. 若没有, 就在任意方向做公式. </p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/en/image40.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"x' R2 D2 (R' U' R D2) R' U R' x\"><strong>x' R2 D2 (R' U' R D2) R' U R' x</strong></span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"M2' U M U2\"><strong>M2' U M U2 </strong></span></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"M' U M2'\"><strong>M' U M2'</strong></span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div>","zh":"<p><strong>三<img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/zh/image3.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">阶魔方层先法 (LBL)</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td rowspan=\"2\"><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/zh/image5.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">结构</strong></p><p>三阶魔方是由匈牙利建筑学教授鲁比克·艾尔内 (Rubik Ernő) 于1974年发明的机械益智玩具. 世界魔方协会WCA承认的单次和平均世界纪录分别是美国人Max Park的3.13秒和中国人王艺衡的4.48秒. 魔方有上下左右前后6个面, 内部是立体十字架结构. 已还原魔方同一面9个格颜色相同. 无论魔方怎样转动, 6个中心相对位置始终不变. 颜色相近相对: 白黄相对, 红橙相对, 蓝绿相对.</p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/zh/image7.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/zh/image9.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"> </p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p> <img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/zh/image11.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><p>6个心</p><p>通过6根轴连接</p><p>每个心有1个格</p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p>12个棱</p><p>每个棱有2个格</p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p>8个角</p><p>每个角有3个格</p></td></tr><tr><td rowspan=\"6\"><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/zh/image13.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">小花</strong></p><p>黄心始终朝上, 可将魔方放桌上.</p><p>二楼找白棱, 转体将白格放前, 用左右手转上去. 若有白棱挡住了去路, 先让开.</p><p>当二楼没有白棱时, 找一或三楼的白棱, 转体将白格放前, 压前层将棱转到二楼, 再用左或右手转上去. </p><p>若白棱的白格在底面 (地下室), 放右, 做上上.</p><p>注: 初学者可不用学习英文转动记号.</p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p>二楼</p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p>二楼，顶面挡住</p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p>二楼</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/zh/image15.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/zh/image17.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/zh/image19.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong>右手上</strong></p><p><strong>R</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong>转顶层让开 右手上</strong></p><p><strong>U* R</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong>左手上</strong></p><p><strong>L'</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><p>三楼</p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p>一楼</p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p>地下室</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/zh/image21.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/zh/image23.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/zh/image25.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong>↓压 -&gt; 二楼</strong></p><p><strong>↓F</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong>↓压 -&gt; 二楼</strong></p><p><strong>↓F</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong>上上</strong></p><p><strong>↓R2</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td rowspan=\"2\"><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/zh/image27.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>十字 (棱)</strong></p><p>左手拿顶层, 右手同时转下面两层, 将白棱前面颜色和心对齐, 转体放在右手边, 做上上. 重复四次, 完成十字.</p></td><td colspan=\"6\"><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/zh/image29.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"6\"><p><strong>对齐转体上上</strong></p><p><strong>y'↓R2</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td rowspan=\"3\"><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/zh/image31.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">底层 (角)</strong></p><p><strong>右公式 = 右手上钩下回</strong></p><p><strong>左公式 = 左手上钩下回</strong></p><p>白格在顶层侧面: 找到这个白角侧面的不是白色的格, 转顶层让这个格朝前, 同时转下面两层将侧面颜色和中心对齐, 做公式.</p></td><td><p>白朝右</p><p>角心对齐</p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p>底层白角</p><p>放右</p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p>白朝左</p><p>角心对齐</p></td><td><p>白朝上</p><p>角心交叉对齐</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/zh/image33.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/zh/image35.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/zh/image37.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/zh/image39.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"3\"><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R U R' U'\"><strong>R U R' U'</strong></span></p><p><strong>右公式</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"L' U' L U\"><strong>L' U' L U</strong></span></p><p><strong>左公式</strong></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"(R U R' U')3\"><strong>(R U R' U')3</strong></span></p><p><strong>右公式三遍</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td rowspan=\"3\"><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/zh/image41.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>中层 (棱)</strong></p><p>顶层找非黄棱, 放前, 同时转下面两层将侧面颜色与中心对齐 (形成倒T), 做公式.</p></td><td><p>去右</p><p>棱心对齐</p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p>中层非黄棱</p><p>放右</p></td><td colspan=\"3\"><p>去左</p><p>棱心对齐</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/zh/image43.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/zh/image45.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td colspan=\"3\"><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/zh/image47.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"3\"><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"U R U R' U' y L' U' L U\"><strong>U R U R' U' y L' U' L U</strong></span></p><p><strong>右手拨 右公式 左转体 左公式</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"3\"><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"U' L' U' L U y' R U R' U'\"><strong>U' L' U' L U y' R U R' U'</strong></span></p><p><strong>左手拨 左公式 右转体 右公式</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td rowspan=\"2\"><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/zh/image49.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">黄十字 (棱色向)</strong></p><p>以下图都是顶层的俯视图. 先转顶层调整到相应角度.</p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/zh/image51.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p>横line</p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/zh/image53.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p>三点半3:30</p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/zh/image55.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p><p>点Dot</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"F R U R' U' F'\"><strong>F R U R' U' F'</strong></span></p><p><strong>压 右公式 提</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"f R U R' U' f'\"><strong>f R U R' U' f'</strong></span></p><p><strong>双压 右公式 双提</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"F R U R' U' F'\"><strong>F R U R' U' F'</strong></span></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"f R U R' U' f'\"><strong>f R U R' U' f'</strong></span></p><p><strong>压 右公式 提</strong></p><p><strong>双压 右公式 双提</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td rowspan=\"4\"><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/zh/image57.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>黄面 (角色向)</strong></p><p>判断顶面灰格个数 (即非黄格). 然后观察时将左拇指贴到前面的左边格上. 以下公式可能不止做一遍. 如果始终不能还原此步, 则需要手动拧角.</p><p><strong>右鱼公式 = 右手 上钩下钩上连拨下</strong></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R U R' U R U2' R'\"><strong>R U R' U R U2' R'</strong></span></p><p><strong>左鱼公式 = 左手 上钩下钩上连拨下</strong></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"L' U' L U' L' U2 L\"><strong>L' U' L U' L' U2 L</strong></span></p></td><td><p>3灰 (右鱼)</p><p>3个鱼鳍朝右</p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p>3灰 (左鱼)</p><p>3个鱼鳍朝左</p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p>2灰 (二碰)</p><p>双头鱼</p></td><td><p>4灰 (四不碰)</p><p>无头鱼</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>鱼头放左前</p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p>鱼头放右前</p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p>转顶层左拇指碰黄</p></td><td><p>转顶层左拇指不碰黄</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/zh/image59.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/zh/image61.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/zh/image63.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"> 2</p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/zh/image65.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong> 4</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R U R' U R U2' R'\"><strong>R U R' U R U2' R'</strong></span></p><p><strong>Right Sune</strong></p><p><strong>右鱼</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"L' U' L U' L' U2 L\"><strong>L' U' L U' L' U2 L</strong></span></p><p><strong>Left Sune</strong></p><p><strong>左鱼公式</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong>右鱼公式 -&gt; 鱼</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>右鱼公式 -&gt; 鱼</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td rowspan=\"2\"><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/zh/image67.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>角位置</strong></p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/zh/image69.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">眼</p><p>该公式称为L公式. </p></td><td colspan=\"3\"><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/zh/image71.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">眼放左<strong> </strong></p></td><td colspan=\"3\"><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/zh/image73.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">无眼</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"6\"><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"(R U R' F') (R U R' U') (R' F R2 U' R')\"><strong>(R U R' F') (R U R' U') (R' F R2 U' R')</strong></span></p></td></tr><tr><td rowspan=\"2\"><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/zh/image75.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>棱位置</strong></p><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/zh/image77.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">墙放后. 如果没有墙, 先做右边任意一个公式.</p></td><td colspan=\"3\"><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/zh/image79.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong> </strong></p><p>adj on R</p><p><strong>Right Sune + U + Left Sune</strong></p><p>对色在左</p></td><td colspan=\"3\"><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/lbl/zh/image81.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong> </strong></p><p>adj on L</p><p><strong>Left Sune + U' + Right Sune</strong></p><p>对色在右</p></td